modName: Kitty's Goddess Pack Standalone CBBE UUNP With Preset's
summary: Adds 5 butt kicking smexy followers to the game. 1 and 2h Nord based, each with their own set of skills.
descriptionHtml:
[center]
[youtube]70cdMAx4sY4[/youtube]

[color=#ffff00][size=3]I decided to revamp my Goddess series and take all four of my previous Goddess followers and redo them. The FaceGen's remained the same with the exception of Dibella who got a total makeover. As a bonus, I added a new Goddess Nocturnal. All five can be found on the platform near the bottom of Lost Valley Redoubt. (coc lostvalleyredoubt01) zaps you near them. (See screens and video). As with my other followers, combat will focus mainly on Melee and Ranged attacks and each lady will possess one destruction spell. Mara will be the only one that doesn't have any spells because she is the healer in the bunch. The healing is non-script-based so the effects will vary depending on battle situations and other things.
[/size][/color]
